contents.summary: Colt is a Common character from Brawl Stars, located in the Green World. As an Attacker, Colt specializes in dealing ranged damage.

classic.name: Classic Ability
classic.description: Bust 4 foes to fire Bullet Storm

super.name: Super Ability
super.description: Bullet Storm deals much more damage

trivia: Colt is named after Samuel Colt, the man who first invented the Colt Revolver, which he uses himself. Colt himself also carries this weapon, as his name suggests.
Colt was the first Brawl Stars character created, designed by a former game designer of Brawl Stars, Paul Chambers.
history: 06/02/2023 - Colt was added to the game by the First Beta (which was closed)

contents.trivia: The hog that he rides is most likely a 'Phacochoerus africanus' (common warthog). Common Warthogs are smaller than boars but more agile which might explain why the Hog Rider can move particularly fast. Warthogs also have tusks, which is like the Hog Rider's hog in Clash of Clans. The Hog Rider bears more than a passing resemblance to Mr. T and Zangief from Street Fighter. The Hog Rider is featured as a character skin for Carl in Brawl Stars.
